Name:         Tardigrade
Scientific:   Ramazzottius varieornatus
Class:        Tardigrada
Habitat:      Everywhere
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     2.5 years
Weight:       1e-07 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Nearly indestructible; survives space vacuum, radiation, extreme temps

Name:         Octopus
Scientific:   Octopus vulgaris
Class:        Cephalopoda
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     3 years
Weight:       10 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         3 hearts, blue blood; changes color in 0.3 seconds; 9 brains

